OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Peter
OL,4,CBelcher
OL,6,FPeter Belcher, Age: 100, Oxfordshire
OL,7,Fand Buckinghamshire Light Infantry
OL,9,FInterviewed 22 February 2024
OL,11,FA paratrooper in the Airborne
OL,12,FRegiment, 4th Battalion Ox and Bucks,
OL,13,FMr Belcher was dropped behind enemy
OL,14,Flines in a wooden glider in the early
OL,15,Fhours of D-Day before the beach
OL,16,Flandings.
OL,18,FHe took off from RAF Harwell in
OL,19,FOxfordshire, part of a crew in the
OL,20,Fglider tasked with manning an anti-
OL,21,Ftank gun.
