OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Peter
OL,4,CBelcher
OL,6,F"Whatever practice you do goes out the
OL,7,Fwindow when the real thing starts," he
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"A Halifax plane was the tow plane -
OL,11,Fthere were six of us on the gun and we
OL,12,Fhad some RAF and artillery observers
OL,13,Fwith wireless sets because the RAF
OL,14,Fwere to bring in planes if we needed
OL,15,Fassistance.
OL,17,F"You're scared to death.
OL,19,F"Whatever training you do it's going
OL,20,Fto be them or you.
