OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Peter
OL,4,CBelcher
OL,6,F"We landed and got everything out of
OL,7,Fthe glider. Luckily it was very quiet
OL,8,Ffor us."
OL,10,FAn Ox and Bucks unit commanded by
OL,11,FMajor John Howard had already taken
OL,12,Froad bridges across the River Orne and
OL,13,Fthe Caen Canal, including Pegasus
OL,14,FBridge.
OL,16,FIn doing so they became the first
OL,17,Ftroops on the ground during the
OL,18,Fliberation of France.
