OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Peter
OL,4,CBelcher
OL,6,FMr Belcher said: "At first there were
OL,7,Fnot a great number of troops. They
OL,8,Fwere further inland. By eight o'clock
OL,9,Fthe next morning was the first time I
OL,10,Factually fired a gun in anger.
OL,12,F"We knocked out two tanks in about
OL,13,Ftwenty minutes. The first time I fired
OL,14,Fat a tank the shot hit it and bounced
OL,15,Foff, ricocheted off. And it's very
OL,16,Ffrightening.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
