OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Peter
OL,4,CBelcher
OL,6,F"The tank stopped and before he got a
OL,7,Fchance to see what was happening we
OL,8,Fhad to get another shot in and we did.
OL,9,FIt burst into flames and the crew
OL,10,Fbailed out.
OL,12,F"One of our members had a machine gun.
OL,13,FIt sounds harsh but this is warfare.
OL,15,F"You don't let people come out of a
OL,16,Ftank and wish them the best of luck.
OL,17,FYou shoot them."
OL,19,FMr Belcher is one of the last veterans
OL,20,Ffrom the Ox and Bucks who saw action
OL,21,Fin Normandy.
